ltsp (5.4.2-2ubuntu2) quantal; urgency=low

  * Add 40-ltsp as 40-ltsp-client and 40-ltsp-server in Xsession.d for both
    ltsp-client-core and ltsp-server. (LP: #987726)
  * Cherry pick commits from upstream:
    - 3274: Allow qemu-debootstrap for foreign architectures
    - 3273: Change path from /tmp/net-* to /run/net-* to match new
      initramfs-tools behaviour
    - 3272: Enable recommends by default on Ubuntu
  * Update fat-client debconf description as it doesn't need translation
    and should only be used for preseeding.

 -- Stéphane Graber <stgraber@ubuntu.com>  Wed, 01 Aug 2012 18:46:26 -0400

