ltsp (5.2.4-0ubuntu2) maverick; urgency=low

  * Update the d-i component to use /media/cdrom instead of /cdrom
    as /cdrom doesn't exist in /target anymore.
  * Set Language field for debconf translation or debconf-updatepo
    will set it to an empty value.

  * Fix .diff.gz issue in -0ubuntu1, these upstream changes weren't
    in the binary package. These were upstream bugfixes and optimisations:
   * udhcp now waits for 0.1s instead of 1s
   * Change ltsp-core's way to start upstart
   * Fix configure_cron's check of /etc/cron.d being writeable
   * Add "Language" tag to most .po files
   * Fix X01-localapps's check of /etc being writeable
   * Get rid of .pc directory
   * Change ltsp-update-sshkeys to use /sbin/ip instead of /sbin/ifconfig

