   * Ubuntu: Disable ureadahead
   * Ubuntu: Add experimental fat-client plugin
   * Improve logout actions
   * Ubuntu: Drop usplash references (in the plugins)
   * Translation update
   * Change VT-switching for flickerless boot
   * Cleanup rdesktop screen output
   * Ubuntu: Drop hal
  * Use upstream ltsp-restart and ltsp-shutdown
  * Remove Intel desktop hack (no longer required)
  * Set -nr as X parameter for flickerless boot

