  * New upstream version (5.1.83)
   * Fix monitor_nbd to use start-stop-daemon
   * Fix hanging session on logout

  [Michael Haas <laga@laga.ath.cx>]
  * Update debian/extra-plugins/030_mythbuntu:
    - Remove --mythbuntu-copy-user-credentials as chpasswd does not
      support encrypted passwords anymore
    - Do not install linux-restricted-modules as it doesn't exist anymore
    - Install mythbuntu-common 

